'''Mnemiotic drugs''' were given to all [[Imperial Intelligence/Legends|Imperial Intelligence]] trainees, [[Soldier/Legends|soldiers]], and [[Assassin/Legends|assassins]] to boost their memory retention rate. Overuse of the drug could cause [[Hallucination/Legends|hallucinations]] and [[Brain/Legends|brain]] damage.

